            * src/powerpc/sysv.S: Remove redundant .globl ffi_prep_args_SYSV.
            (ffi_call_SYSV): Make hidden.  Replace hand-written .eh_frame with
            .cfi directives.  Adjust for changed params.  Pass extra "closure"
